    junit.framework.Test

    public class Bigdata2ASTSPARQL11SyntaxTest
extends org.openrdf.query.parser.sparql.manifest.SPARQL11SyntaxTest
    Bigdata integration for the SPARQLSyntaxTest. This appears to be a manifest driven test suite for both correct acceptance and correct rejection tests of the SPARQL parser. There is also an Earl report for this test suite which provides a W3C markup for the test results. The Earl report is part of the Sesame compliance packages.
    Author:
    Bryan Thompson
